---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Terms of Service"
  description="Terms of service for Bay Navigator - a community resource by Bay Tides."
>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container-page">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-neutral-900 dark:text-white mb-6">
          Terms of Service
        </h1>

        <p class="text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-400 mb-8">
          Last updated: January 2, 2026
        </p>

        <div class="prose dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 dark:text-white mt-8 mb-4">
            Summary
          </h2>
          <div class="bg-primary-50 dark:bg-primary-900/20 border-l-4 border-primary-500 p-4 rounded-r-lg mb-6">
            <p class="text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300">
              Bay Navigator is a free resource listing programs in the Bay Area. We try to keep information accurate, but always verify details with the program directly. Don't rely solely on this site for important decisions.
            </p>
          </div>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 dark:text-white mt-8 mb-4">
            Acceptance of Terms
          </h2>
          <p class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-300 mb-6">
            By accessing Bay Navigator (the "Service"), you agree to these terms. If you don't agree, please don't use the Service.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 dark:text-white mt-8 mb-4">
            Description of Service
          </h2>
          <p class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-300 mb-4">
            Bay Navigator is a free, community-maintained directory of programs offering free or discounted services in the San Francisco Bay Area. The Service is provided by Bay Tides, a 501(c)(3) nonprofit organization.
          </p>
          <p class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-300 mb-6">
            The Service includes:
          </p>
          <ul class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-300 space-y-2 mb-6">
            <li>A searchable directory of programs</li>
            <li>Eligibility guides for common benefit programs</li>
            <li>Mobile applications for iOS and Android</li>
            <li>An AI-powered assistant to help find relevant programs</li>
          </ul>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 dark:text-white mt-8 mb-4">
            No Warranties
          </h2>
          <p class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-300 mb-4">
            The Service is provided "as is" without warranties of any kind. We make no guarantees that:
          </p>
          <ul class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-300 space-y-2 mb-6">
            <li>Information is complete, accurate, or up-to-date</li>
            <li>Programs listed are currently accepting applications</li>
            <li>You will qualify for any particular program</li>
            <li>The Service will be available without interruption</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-300 mb-6">
            <strong>Always verify program details, eligibility requirements, and application procedures directly with the program provider.</strong>
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 dark:text-white mt-8 mb-4">
            Limitation of Liability
          </h2>
          <p class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-300 mb-6">
            Bay Tides and its volunteers shall not be liable for any damages arising from your use of the Service, including but not limited to: missed program deadlines, incorrect eligibility information, denial of benefits, or any other direct or indirect damages.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 dark:text-white mt-8 mb-4">
            AI Assistant Disclaimer
          </h2>
          <p class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-300 mb-6">
            The Smart Assistant feature uses artificial intelligence to help you find programs. AI responses are suggestions only and may contain errors. Always verify information with official program sources before making decisions.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 dark:text-white mt-8 mb-4">
            User Conduct
          </h2>
          <p class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-300 mb-4">
            You agree not to:
          </p>
          <ul class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-300 space-y-2 mb-6">
            <li>Use the Service for any unlawful purpose</li>
            <li>Attempt to gain unauthorized access to our systems</li>
            <li>Scrape or collect data in bulk without permission</li>
            <li>Interfere with the proper operation of the Service</li>
            <li>Use the AI assistant for purposes unrelated to finding programs</li>
          </ul>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 dark:text-white mt-8 mb-4">
            Intellectual Property
          </h2>
          <p class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-300 mb-4">
            The Bay Navigator codebase is open source under the MIT License. You may use, modify, and distribute the code according to that license.
          </p>
          <p class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-300 mb-6">
            The program data is provided under a separate license (see LICENSE-DATA in our repository). The Bay Navigator name and logo are trademarks of Bay Tides.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 dark:text-white mt-8 mb-4">
            Third-Party Links
          </h2>
          <p class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-300 mb-6">
            The Service contains links to external websites. We are not responsible for the content, policies, or practices of any third-party sites. Linking to a site does not imply endorsement.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 dark:text-white mt-8 mb-4">
            Modifications
          </h2>
          <p class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-300 mb-6">
            We may modify these terms at any time. Continued use of the Service after changes constitutes acceptance of the new terms. Material changes will be announced on our GitHub repository.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 dark:text-white mt-8 mb-4">
            Termination
          </h2>
          <p class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-300 mb-6">
            We reserve the right to terminate or suspend access to the Service at any time, for any reason, without notice.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 dark:text-white mt-8 mb-4">
            Governing Law
          </h2>
          <p class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-300 mb-6">
            These terms are governed by the laws of the State of California, United States, without regard to conflict of law principles.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 dark:text-white mt-8 mb-4">
            Contact
          </h2>
          <p class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-300 mb-6">
            Questions about these terms can be directed to hello [at] baytides [dot] org or through <a href="https://github.com/baytides/baynavigator/issues">GitHub</a>.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-12">
          <a href="/" class="btn-secondary">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 19l-7-7m0 0l7-7m-7 7h18"/>
            </svg>
            Back to Programs
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
